=head1 DESCRIPTION

Contains information for HTTP-based domain validation of certificates
requested through CloudFront and issued by ACM. This field exists only
when the certificate type is C<AMAZON_ISSUED> and the validation method
is C<HTTP>.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 RedirectFrom => Str

The URL including the domain to be validated. The certificate authority
sends C<GET> requests here during validation.


=head2 RedirectTo => Str

The URL hosting the validation token. C<RedirectFrom> must return this
content or redirect here.



